### Admin User Journey - Minimal API Requests

### 1. Login as Admin
# @name adminLogin
POST https://localhost:9000/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@system.local",
  "password": "Test@1234"
}

###

### 2. Get Current Admin User
# @name currentAdmin
GET https://localhost:9000/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}

###

### 3. Get Admin Permissions
GET https://localhost:9000/api/users/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}

###

### 4. Create Mathematics Category
POST https://localhost:9000/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminLogin.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Mathematics",
  "displayInLandingPage": true
}

###

### 5. Create Science Category
POST https://localhost:9000/api/categories
